                        "id": "18174171973359816",
                        "text": "Comment \u201cLoft\u201d for a Google Map link of the store!\n\nIf you\u2019re already shopped at Donki or the Beams store and want another spot for cool gifts, don\u2019t forget to check out LOFT!\n\nIf Donki is the Walmart of Japan, LOFT is more like the Target of Japan. Cleaner aesthetic, better merchandising, and higher quality products. \n\nThis six floor building has a great selection of stationery, home goods, beauty/skincare, watches, and travel bags so come here if you\u2019re looking for those. The quality is a step up, and you\u2019ll products at all price points!\n\u2014\n#tokyogift #tokyostyle #tokyotravel #traveling #traveljapan #fashion #madeinjapan #japanesegifts"
                    }
                }
            ]
